\v 1 Bathandekayo, lingakholwa wonke umoya\x + Mat. 24.4.\x*, kodwa hlolani\x + 1 Thes. 5.21. 1 Kor. 2.15; 12.10; 14.29. 2 Kor. 11.13.\x* omoya\x + 2 Thes. 2.2.\x*, ukuthi bavela kuNkulunkulu yini; ngoba banengi\x + 2.18. Isam. 2.2.\x* abaprofethi bamanga abaphumele emhlabeni\x + Mat. 7.15. Isam. 16.13.\x*.
\v 2 Ngalokhu liyamazi uMoya kaNkulunkulu: Wonke umoya ovumayo\x + 4.15. 5.1. 1 Kor. 12.3.\x* ukuthi uJesu Kristu uzile enyameni, uvela kuNkulunkulu\x + 1 Tim. 3.16. Joha. 1.14.\x*;
\v 3 futhi wonke umoya ongavumiyo\x + 2.22. 2 Joha. 1.7.\x* ukuthi uJesu Kristu usezile enyameni, kaveli kuNkulunkulu\x + 1 Tim. 3.16. Joha. 1.14.\x*; lalo ungowomphikuKristu\x + 2.18.\x*, eselizwile ukuthi uyeza, lakhathesi usekhona emhlabeni\x + 2.18,22. 2 Thes. 2.3,7.\x*.
