\v 4 Lina lingabakaNkulunkulu, bantwanyana, futhi libanqobile\x + 5.4.\x*; ngoba mkhulu okini\x + Roma 8.31.\x* kulalowo osemhlabeni\x + Joha. 12.31. 1 Kor. 2.12.\x*.
\v 5 Bona bangabomhlaba\x + Joha. 8.23. Joha. 3.31.\x*; ngenxa yalokho bakhuluma okuvela emhlabeni, njalo umhlaba uyabezwa\x + Joha. 15.19.\x*.
\v 6 Thina singabakaNkulunkulu; omaziyo uNkulunkulu, uyasizwa\x + Joha. 8.47; 10.27; 18.37. Isa. 8.20. 1 Kor. 14.37. 2 Kor. 10.7.\x*; ongeyisuye kaNkulunkulu, kasizwa\x + Joha. 8.47; 10.27; 18.37. Isa. 8.20. 1 Kor. 14.37. 2 Kor. 10.7.\x*. Ngalokhu siyamazi umoya weqiniso\x + Joha. 14.17.\x* lomoya wokuduha\x + 1 Tim. 4.1.\x*.
\s Ukuthanda uNkulunkulu lokuthanda abantu
\p
\v 7 Bathandekayo, asithandaneni\x + 3.11.\x*; ngoba uthando luvela kuNkulunkulu, laye wonke othandayo, uzelwe nguNkulunkulu, futhi uyamazi uNkulunkulu.
\v 8 Ongathandiyo\x + 3.10.\x*, kamazi uNkulunkulu\x + 3.6. 2.4.\x*; ngoba uNkulunkulu uluthando\x + 4.16. 4.7. 2 Kor. 13.11.\x*.
\v 9 Ngalokhu uthando lukaNkulunkulu lwabonakaliswa kithi\x + 4.16. 3.16.\x*, ukuthi uNkulunkulu wathuma iNdodana yakhe ezelwe yodwa emhlabeni\x + Joha. 3.16.\x*, ukuze siphile ngayo\x + 5.11.\x*.
\v 10 Uthando lukulokhu, kungesikuthi thina samthanda uNkulunkulu\x + 4.19. Joha. 15.16. Roma 5.8,10.\x*, kodwa ukuthi yena wasithanda\x + 3.1. 2 Thes. 2.16.\x*, wasethuma iNdodana yakhe \add ukuthi ibe\add* yinhlawulo yokuthula ngezono zethu\x + 2.2.\x*.
\v 11 Bathandekayo, uba uNkulunkulu wasithanda ngokunje, lathi sifanele ukuthandana\x + Joha. 13.34. Mat. 18.33.\x*.
\v 12 Kakulamuntu owake wabona uNkulunkulu\x + 4.20. Joha. 1.18.\x*; uba sithandana, uNkulunkulu uhlala kithi\x + 2.24.\x*, lothando lwakhe luphelelisiwe kithi\x + 2.5. 4.18.\x*.
\v 13 Ngalokhu siyazi ukuthi\x + 2.5.\x* sihlala kuye, laye kithi\x + 3.24. Joha. 5.38.\x*\x + 2.24.\x*, ngoba usinikile okukaMoya wakhe\x + 3.24. Joha. 5.38.\x*.
\v 14 Thina sesibonile\x + 1.1.\x* siyafakaza\x + 1.2.\x* ukuthi uYise uyithumile iNdodana\x + Joha. 3.17. Mat. 18.11.\x* \add ibe\add* nguMsindisi womhlaba\x + 2.2. Joha. 4.42. 1 Tim. 4.10.\x*.
\v 15 Loba ngubani ovumayo\x + 4.2. 2.23.\x* ukuthi uJesu uyiNdodana kaNkulunkulu\x + 5.5. Mat. 14.33.\x*, uNkulunkulu uhlala kuye, laye kuNkulunkulu\x + 2.24.\x*.
\v 16 Thina sesisazi sakholwa uthando uNkulunkulu alalo kithi\x + 4.9.\x*. UNkulunkulu uluthando\x + 4.8.\x*, njalo ohlala ethandweni uhlala kuNkulunkulu, loNkulunkulu kuye\x + 2.24.\x*.
