\v 18 Kakukho ukwesaba ethandweni, kodwa uthando olupheleleyo luyaxotsha ukwesaba\x + Roma 8.15.\x*, ngoba ukwesaba kulobuhlungu; lowesabayo kapheleliswanga ethandweni\x + 2.5. 4.18.\x*.
\v 19 Thina siyamthanda, ngoba yena wasithanda kuqala\x + 4.10.\x*.
